
extends layout



block main-content   
    .background-container.mb-4
        nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.bg-body-tertiary.fixed-top
            .container-fluid
                a.navbar-brand.fontStyle.fs-2.mx-auto(href="/") My Home
                button.navbar-toggler(type="button", data-bs-toggle="collapse", data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent", aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent", aria-expanded="false", aria-label="Toggle navigation")
                    span.navbar-toggler-icon
                .collapse.navbar-collapse.text1(id="navbarSupportedContent")
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.fs-5(aria-current="page", href="/") Home
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.fs-5(href="/shop") Shop
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.fs-5(href="/news") News      
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.active.fs-5(href="/about") About
                        li.nav-item 
                            a.nav-link(href="/cart")
                                img(src="/images/cart-shopping-solid.svg", alt="Add to Cart", style="max-width: 1.5rem; height: auto; min-width:1.4rem;")     
        .about-section
            h1 
                strong About Us
            p Experienced and Friendly
    .container.mt-5
        .row.justify-content-center
            .col-md-4.mb-4
                .d-flex.justify-content-center
                    img.img-fluid(src="/images/pencil4 Background Removed.png", alt="500+ UI Components Image")
                .card.border-0
                    .card-body.mb-3
                        h2.card-title.fs-4 DARK AND LIGHT
                        p.card-text Immerse yourself in the art of contrast with our "Dark and Light" collection. This curated selection harmonizes shadows and highlights, offering a balance of sophistication and warmth. 
                        a.btn.text-dark(href="#") READ MORE
                            span.ms-1
                                img(src="/images/arrow Background Removed.png", alt="arrow")
            .col-md-4.mb-4
                .d-flex.justify-content-center
                    img.img-fluid(src="/images/brush Background Removed.png", alt="500+ UI Components Image")
                .card.border-0
                    .card-body.mb-3
                        h2.card-title.fs-4 FULLY RESPONSIVE
                        p.card-text Experience the epitome of adaptability with our "Fully Responsive" range. Each piece is meticulously designed to seamlessly integrate into your living spaces. 
                        a.btn.text-dark(href="#") READ MORE
                            span.ms-1
                                img(src="/images/arrow Background Removed.png", alt="arrow")                   
    .container-fluid.mt-5.bg-dark
        .row
            .col-md-6.position-relative
                .bg-light.p-4.position-relative
                    h2 Our Company
                    p.
                        At 'My Home,' our passion for transforming spaces into personalized
                        sanctuaries drives us to bring you a unique blend of elegance and functionality. Nestled within
                        the heart of home decor, our journey began with a vision to curate spaces that resonate with
                        individual styles. Our team, united by a shared love for design, carefully selects each piece to
                        tell a story. From timeless classics to contemporary marvels, we believe in crafting homes that
                        reflect your personality. Beyond aesthetics, our commitment extends to quality and
                        craftsmanship, ensuring that every item finds its perfect place in your home. Join us on this
                        journey of creating harmonious living spaces that truly feel like 'home.'
            .col-md-6.position-relative
                img.img-fluid.company-image(src="/images/aboutus.jpeg", alt="Company Image")
    .container.mt-5
        h2.text-center.mb-4.fontStyle Meet Our Professional Team
        .row
            .col-md-3.mb-4
                .card.team-card
                    img.card-img-top(src="images/member1.jpeg", alt="Team Member 1")
                    .card-body.text-center
                        h5.card-title John Doe
                        p.card-text Interior Designer
            .col-md-3.mb-4
                .card.team-card
                    img.card-img-top(src="/images/member2.jpeg", alt="Team Member 1")
                    .card-body.text-center
                        h5.card-title Jane Smith
                        p.card-text Project Manager
            .col-md-3.mb-4
                .card.team-card
                    img.card-img-top(src="/images/member3.jpeg", alt="Team Member 1")
                    .card-body.text-center
                        h5.card-title Mike Johnson
                        p.card-text Customer Service Representative
            .col-md-3.mb-4
                .card.team-card
                    img.card-img-top(src="/images/mem.jpeg", alt="Team Member 1")
                    .card-body.text-center
                        h5.card-title Emily Davis
                        p.card-text Graphic Designer    

                                                      
                        
        